nd professional growth.</p>','<h4 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-12a1e5m\">Aims of the Diploma</h4>\r\n<p class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1ahpl9\">The diploma aims to:</p>\r\n<ul class=\"framer-text\">\r\n<li class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1ahpl9\" data-preset-tag=\"p\">Develop technical knowledge in core areas of IT, including operating systems, ethics, and database management.</li>\r\n<li class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1ahpl9\" data-preset-tag=\"p\">Enable learners to apply analytical and evaluative skills in a variety of IT contexts.</li>\r\n<li class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1ahpl9\" data-preset-tag=\"p\">Support progression into technical positions or higher-level IT study pathways.</li>\r\n<li class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-1ahpl9\" data-preset-tag=\"p\">Enhance skills such as problem-solving, independent research, and collaboration, critical to the IT sector.</li>\r\n</ul>',11900,0,1,1,'active',1,'2025-06-13 07:53:59','2025-06-19 12:24:53',1),(3,'Law','Law',8,2,'603/4781/8','120 ECTS','uploads/courses/course_thumbnail_684feb04b87b8.jpg','uploads/courses/course_logo_684feb04b8a54.jpg','uploads/courses/handbook_684bf5372ad5f.pdf','uploads/courses/mapping_document_684bf5372af73.pdf','uploads/courses/assignment_specification_684bf5372b15a.pdf','uploads/courses/curriculum_684bf5372b315.pdf','youtube','https://youtu.be/sVPYIRF9RCQ?si=labNkx-xlyOWtptr','<p>test</p>','<p>The Level 4 Diploma in Information Technology is designed to provide learners with a strong foundational knowledge across key areas of IT, including PC maintenance, programming, and database management. This diploma equips students for entry-level IT roles or progression to higher-level studies in specialised fields such as networking, software development, and web design. It combines practical and theoretical learning to foster essential technical skills for the modern IT industry.</p>','<h4 class=\"framer-text framer-styles-preset-12a1e5m\"